# command-mode journey: :new (opens read mode), then base switching
# let the layout settle
2.0 n
0.3 n
0.3 \r
# viewing a note; close it back to the graph with :q
1.5 :
0.2 q
0.2 \r
# :new scratch/probe -> creates the note and opens it in read mode
0.8 :
0.2 new scratch/probe
0.3 \r
# close the new note back to the graph
1.0 :
0.2 q
0.2 \r
# cycle base with 'b' twice, then :base daily, then quit the app
1.2 b
0.8 b
0.8 :
0.2 base daily
0.2 \r
1.0 :
0.2 q
0.2 \r
